<HEADLINE> Hong Kong Shares Close Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, November 12 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong stocks fell 396.22
points, or 3.96 percent, to close at 9,607.91 today. 
