are still here: the Basic Law guarantees our independence, the
anti-corruption laws are intact and the new administration and the
people of Hong Kong are solidly behind us," she said.
</P>
<P>
A total of 33 delegates from 23 agencies in 16 jurisdictions
attended the seminar, the first of its kind held in the
post-handover Hong Kong.
