On one hand the U.S. had supported Israel, while on the other hand
it sometimes took military actions against Arab countries.
</P>
<P>
As a superpower, the U.S. should be ashamed of attacking Iraq,
he said.
</P>
<P>
he said the U.S. action against Iraq was tantamount to human
rights violations.
</P>
<P>
"I think that Iraqi people have much sacrificed. Let us not add
another suffering. The Iraq government should concentrate on
developing the economy. We hope that the Organization of Islamic
Conference will play a bigger role in the matter," he added.
</P>
